<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>中国新闻|今日突发新闻 |路透社</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china/</link><description>Reuters.com 是您获取最新中国新闻故事和时事的在线来源，确保我们的读者及时了解任何突发新闻动态 - RSSHub 用爱制作(https://github.com/DIYgod/RSSHub)</description><lastBuildDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 09:11:55 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>丰田在泰国主要市场试点电动皮卡车</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/toyota-pilots-ev-pickup-trucks-key-thai-market-2024-04-25/</link><description>周四，丰田在泰国推出了九辆全电动 Hilux Revo 皮卡的公共交通试点项目，泰国是东南亚电动汽车的一个重要战场，中国企业正在泰国挑战日本汽车制造商的主导地位。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 09:03:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/toyota-pilots-ev-pickup-trucks-key-thai-market-2024-04-25/</guid></item><item><title>中国最大车展展示全电动未来，本土品牌占主导地位</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-largest-auto-show-showcases-all-electric-future-local-brands-dominate-2024-04-25/</link><description>中国最大的车展周四在北京开幕，各大品牌展示了他们最新的电动汽车（EV），突显出全球最大的汽车市场已经处于全电动状态，并且不会回头。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 07:26:18 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinas-largest-auto-show-showcases-all-electric-future-local-brands-dominate-2024-04-25/</guid></item><item><title>中国电动汽车电池制造商CATL推出续航里程达1000公里的磷酸铁锂电池</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-ev-battery-maker-catl-unveils-lfp-battery-with-1000-km-range-2024-04-25/</link><description>中国电动汽车 (EV) 电池制造商宁德时代 (CATL) 周四推出了一款磷酸铁锂 (LFP) 电池，一次充电可行驶超过 1,000 公里（621 英里）。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 06:41:31 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-ev-battery-maker-catl-unveils-lfp-battery-with-1000-km-range-2024-04-25/</guid></item><item><title>独家：中国石化在竞争对手印度后院建设炼油厂，规划全球扩张</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/chinas-sinopec-charts-global-expansion-with-refinery-rival-indias-backyard-2024-04-25/</link><description>中国国有能源巨头中石化正在推动更多地进入斯里兰卡市场，其竞争对手印度也在寻求扩大其影响力，因为它希望建立其第一家完全控股的海外炼油厂，这反映出该公司全球战略的变化，以弥补斯里兰卡的不足。国内需求增长放缓。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 06:26:57 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/commodities/chinas-sinopec-charts-global-expansion-with-refinery-rival-indias-backyard-2024-04-25/</guid></item><item><title>爱马仕第一季度销售额因中国需求强劲增长17%</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/hermes-q1-sales-jump-17-growth-across-regions-2024-04-25/</link><description>铂金包制造商爱马仕周四报告称，第一季度销售额猛增 17%，维持了上一季度（包括中国）的快速增长，突显了高端奢侈品的强劲需求。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 06:05:06 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/hermes-q1-sales-jump-17-growth-across-regions-2024-04-25/</guid></item><item><title>由于订单和广告收入不断增加，Delivery Hero 上调了收入指引</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/delivery-hero-ups-revenue-guidance-after-q1-beat-2024-04-25/</link><description>德国在线外卖食品公司Delivery Hero周四上调了今年的收入预期，此前该公司公布第一季度增长好于预期，原因是订单和广告收入不断增加。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 05:46:36 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/delivery-hero-ups-revenue-guidance-after-q1-beat-2024-04-25/</guid></item><item><title>由于美国和中国拖累销售，保乐力加预计第四季度将“充满活力”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/pernod-ricard-banks-dynamic-q4-after-weaker-than-expected-q3-sales-2024-04-25/</link><description>保乐力加周四公布的第三季度销售额低于预期，因其美国和中国的大型业务仍面临巨大压力，其全年预测取决于未来几个月的需求上升。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 05:24:53 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/pernod-ricard-banks-dynamic-q4-after-weaker-than-expected-q3-sales-2024-04-25/</guid></item><item><title>独家：卫星图像显示，中国停泊与朝俄武器转让有关的船只</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-harbors-ship-tied-north-korea-russia-arms-transfers-satellite-images-show-2024-04-25/</link><description>路透社获得的卫星图像显示，随着美国对北京支持莫斯科乌克兰战争的担忧日益加剧，中国正在为一艘受美国制裁的俄罗斯货船提供停泊地，这艘货船涉及朝鲜向俄罗斯转让武器。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 05:11:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-harbors-ship-tied-north-korea-russia-arms-transfers-satellite-images-show-2024-04-25/</guid></item><item><title>俄罗斯程序员玩“猫捉老鼠”游戏智取审查</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/russian-programmers-play-cat-mouse-game-outsmart-censors-2024-04-25/</link><description>安东尼·鲁德科夫斯基 (Antony Rudkovsky) 15 岁左右时，他开始自学如何构建虚拟专用网络 (VPN)，以访问俄罗斯无法访问的互联网内容。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 05:08:10 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/europe/russian-programmers-play-cat-mouse-game-outsmart-censors-2024-04-25/</guid></item><item><title>丰田、日产与腾讯、百度联手进军中国人工智能军备竞赛</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/toyota-says-partner-with-tencent-china-2024-04-25/</link><description>两家公司周四表示，日本丰田汽车将与中国腾讯合作，日产汽车将与百度合作，跨境合作凸显了人工智能对汽车制造商的重要性。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 04:40:19 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/toyota-says-partner-with-tencent-china-2024-04-25/</guid></item><item><title>中国坚持经济数据，称国防支出“透明”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/world/china-stands-by-economic-data-says-defence-spending-transparent-2024-04-25/</link><description>中国为其经济数据的真实性进行了辩护，并声称其军费开支“透明合理”，同时驳斥了美国印太司令部司令本周发表的“典型的双重标准”言论。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 04:22:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/world/china-stands-by-economic-data-says-defence-spending-transparent-2024-04-25/</guid></item><item><title>数据显示，苹果一季度出货量下降6.6%，失去中国市场第一宝座</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-loses-top-spot-china-market-with-shipments-down-66-q1-data-shows-2024-04-25/</link><description>研究公司 IDC 周四的初步数据显示，由于激烈的竞争，苹果公司在 2024 年第一季度失去了中国最大智能手机销售商的桂冠，因为其智能手机出货量同比下降 6.6%。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 04:14:04 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/technology/apple-loses-top-spot-china-market-with-shipments-down-66-q1-data-shows-2024-04-25/</guid></item><item><title>梅赛德斯-奔驰将为中国市场推出豪华电动货车</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/mercedes-benz-launch-luxury-electric-van-chinese-market-2024-04-25/</link><description>梅赛德斯-奔驰货车部门负责人告诉德国杂志《WirtschaftsWoche》，梅赛德斯-奔驰计划在其 VAN.EA 平台上为中国市场推出一款豪华电动货车。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 04:10:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/mercedes-benz-launch-luxury-electric-van-chinese-market-2024-04-25/</guid></item><item><title>小鹏汽车CEO称软件、AI升级进入“超快周期”</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/xpeng-ceo-says-its-software-ai-upgrades-enter-super-fast-cycle-2024-04-25/</link><description>中国电动汽车(EV)制造商小鹏汽车周四表示，其软件和人工智能培训升级将从5月份开始进入“超快周期”，并希望其平台的使用范围将扩大到其他亚洲国家和欧洲。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 03:55:14 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/xpeng-ceo-says-its-software-ai-upgrades-enter-super-fast-cycle-2024-04-25/</guid></item><item><title>中国电动汽车初创公司蔚来为新版ET7轿车设定起价</title><link>https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-ev-startup-nio-sets-starting-price-new-version-et7-sedan-2024-04-25/</link><description>中国电动汽车 (EV) 初创公司 Nio 首席执行官周四表示，已将新版 ET7 轿车的起价定为 428,000 元人民币（59,063 美元）。</description><pubDate>Thu, 25 Apr 2024 02:56:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.reuters.com/business/autos-transportation/chinese-ev-startup-nio-sets-starting-price-new-version-et7-sedan-2024-04-25/</guid></item></channel></rss>